{"tid":1132552,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"（大爆炸）Galaxy Note 10 Pro 電池流出 容量達 4,500mAh","createTime":"2019-04-30T11:28:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-01T11:32:46.000Z","uid":50534,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e26e74eb2e953ae74016fc94bd215433ae8fe6b0","tid":1132552,"uid":50534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T11:28:25.000Z","msg":"經過 Galaxy Note 7 電池事故後，Samsung 曾經一度將手機電池容量調低，但經過一段日子提升質量和產品監控後，手機電池容量有望再度提升。消息指今年稍後發表的 Galaxy Note 10 將會有多達 4 個型號，其中 Galaxy Note 10 Pro 更會配備系列中容量最大的電池。<br />\n<br />\n來源：gizmochina<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日前一幅宣稱是 Galaxy Note 10 Pro 的電池相片在網上流傳，該電池型號為 EB-BN975ABU，當中的「N975」就是早前傳聞 Galaxy Note 10 Pro 的型號 SM-N975，相信電池正正是為這部旗艦手機而設。這枚電池的容量高達 4,500mAh，比起去年上市 Galaxy Note 9 的 4,000mAh 更大，不過消息指，只有 Pro 版才會獲得電池升級，其他版本仍然維持去年的 4,000mAh 電池容量。<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/04/30/galaxy-note10-pros-battery-bigger-than-the-galaxy-note9/mobile-phone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F04%2F30%2Fgalaxy-note10-pros-battery-bigger-than-the-galaxy-note9%2Fmobile-phone%2F&d=jZUVzsr%2BlXwf2hbAbvJm1WZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=85d0e983\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/04/30/galaxy-note10-pros-battery-bigger-than-the-galaxy-note9/mobile-phone/</a>"},{"pid":"365d334300320b65453c257bb98be98f4aa2fdb6","tid":1132552,"uid":34213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T11:32:25.000Z","msg":"qc2.0?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"435ceeadbdb7cd65a0d5ecfbedc403bf7288f9ba","tid":1132552,"uid":216417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T14:45:32.000Z","msg":"note 10 pro 同s10 5g 同一款電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"692b2a418bb988e6b